exceptions.exn: In environment A : Type f, g, h : A -> A x : nat a : A e : env A H : forall a : A, f (g a) = g (h a) Unable to unify "map h e" with "map g e".

In environment H0 : forall (A B : Type) (f : A -> B) (x : nat) (a : A) (b : B) (e : env A), f a = b -> map f (insert x a e) = insert x b (map f e) A : Type f, g, h : A -> A x : nat a : A e : env A H : forall a : A, f (g a) = g (h a) Unable to unify "f (g ?M1885) = g (h ?M1885)" with "map f (insert x a (map g e)) = insert x (f a) (map g (map h e))".
